Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: entify
Version: v0.4.0
Summary: entify - entify is a program designed to extract using regular expressions all the entities from the files on different resources. This software also provides an interface to look for these entities in any given text.
Home-page: http://github.com/i3visio/entify
Author: Felix Brezo and Yaiza Rubio
Author-email: contacto@i3visio.com
License: COPYING
